hosa &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( kannada : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 1982 kannada romantic drama film directed by dorai - bhagwan duo . it is based on the novel of the same name by vani . the film starred rajkumar , saritha and k. s. ashwath in lead roles . the film was a musical blockbuster with all the songs composed by m. ranga rao considered to be evergreen hits . he was awarded with the state award for best music director for the year &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; .